name: Rocket Cat
description: Rocket Cat is an oscilloscope-themed robot that is part of the WebtrES club. With its forest green box and classic buttons, it stands out among its robotic peers. Its arms and legs are designed in the shape of rockets, allowing it to move swiftly and seamlessly. The screen of Rocket Cat features an adorable cat design, adding a touch of charm to its overall appearance. This robot possesses a unique combination of traits that make it both functional and visually appealing.
